import React from 'react'
  import { MDXTag } from '@mdx-js/tag'
  import { Playground, PropsTable } from 'docz'
import Input from '../app/components/input'

export default ({components, ...props}) => <MDXTag name="wrapper"  components={components}>
<MDXTag name="h1" components={components} props={{"id":"button"}}><MDXTag name="a" components={components} parentName="h1" props={{"aria-hidden":true,"href":"#button"}}><MDXTag name="span" components={components} parentName="a" props={{"className":"icon-link"}}>{`#`}</MDXTag></MDXTag>{`Button`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="h2" components={components} props={{"id":"preperties-table"}}><MDXTag name="a" components={components} parentName="h2" props={{"aria-hidden":true,"href":"#preperties-table"}}><MDXTag name="span" components={components} parentName="a" props={{"className":"icon-link"}}>{`#`}</MDXTag></MDXTag>{`Preperties Table`}</MDXTag>
<PropsTable of={Input} />
<MDXTag name="h2" components={components} props={{"id":"playground"}}><MDXTag name="a" components={components} parentName="h2" props={{"aria-hidden":true,"href":"#playground"}}><MDXTag name="span" components={components} parentName="a" props={{"className":"icon-link"}}>{`#`}</MDXTag></MDXTag>{`Playground`}</MDXTag>
<Playground __position={1} __code={`<Input />`} __scope={{props,Input}}>
      <Input />
</Playground></MDXTag>
